'''Operation: Rebel Hunt''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] military operation enacted during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The military campaign was intended to remove all [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] cells from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Yetnis]]. Its [[Commander/Legends|commander]] was [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Ril Garn]].

